    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Corporate Chaos!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You are an office worker who has discovered that all of your co-workers have been replaced by robots! Climb the office tower and battle the bots with whatever you can get your hands on. Confront the ByteBoss before it’s too late!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Throw your way to victory!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3312600/extras/5e0bbc9a1278e268a180889bade53392.avif?t=1737159078\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3312600/extras_big/5e0bbc9a1278e268a180889bade53392.avif?t=1737159078 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use office supplies and the broken bodies of the bots to bash your way up the office tower.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Battle Rampaging Robots!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3312600/extras/2045f574ceb787df8b0eb620286e7bf0.avif?t=1737159078\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3312600/extras_big/2045f574ceb787df8b0eb620286e7bf0.avif?t=1737159078 width=800 height=470 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fight against the forces of automation! Three unique bosses stand between you and full employment!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Corporate Chaos was created by a team of talented middle and high school students as part of the Hackingtons Game Dev Team.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
